short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Outback Equipment Searcher: Administration and Management Tool.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Outback Equipment Searcher is a management tool designed to increase efficiency and boost productivity in administration processes for Maropost based eCommerce platform - OutbackEquipment Pty Ltd.

Features:
• Security – Secure access to administrative features for users with valid credentials. 
• Accessibility – Quick front-end to back-end access of product and stock information for valid administrative users.
• Margins – Fast rendering of margin data on product pages for valid administrative users.
• Searchability – Search availability of any products or product-ranges in OutbackEquipment eCommerce platform using any selected keywords.

Outback Equipment Searcher – (Version 1.4.0)
